                    "text": "5 feet. Grasping tendrils extend out from the thrall. When the thrall ends its movement next to a creature, or a creature ends its turn next to the thrall, that creature must succeed at a DC 14 Reflex save or be <a aonid=\"20\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">grabbed</a> by the tendrils."
